nodes.text: Oznek was a planet located in the Cademimu sector of the Outer Rim Territories.

Oznek was the homeworld of the sentient Toma species. During the Clone Wars, in 22 BBY, Oznek was the site of a supposed droid command center for the Confederacy of Independent Systems. The Galactic Republic sent a squad of clone troopers to destroy the command center, led by Clone Sergeant Banks. When Commander Griebs Kishpaugh attempted to subvert the mission through his agent, the clone trooper Ghost, Banks stopped the plot.
